      "comment": "GAMADALE INDI (2) doesn't win out of turn wasn't far away fresh when finding a couple better over 1000m at Colac. Strips fitter and is yet to miss the frame over this trip. BARE TO WITNESS (5) battled into third when resuming at long odds at Pakenham. This isn't as tough and should improve with that run under his belt. Backs up quickly and is in the mix. DEEP CORE (7) hasn't won for a very long time and perhaps didn't appreciate the softer conditions last time at Colac but is suited back at this level and gets a key booking in Crowther. Worth monitoring. JUST WAI (8) didn't fire a shot at the latest but was good two back when leading them up at Naracoorte. Senior hoop going on is a push for his chances. Keeping safe.",
